PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1778234502
OL,3,CAppeal for victims of sex-offender
OL,4,Cformer Bishop after further reports
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FThe offences took place whilst he was
OL,8,Fworking as a parish priest at Holy
OL,9,FCross Church in West Cross. Pierce
OL,10,Fchristened his victim as a child,
OL,11,Fbefore going on to abuse him years
OL,12,Flater.
OL,14,FHe was sentenced to four years and one
OL,15,Fmonth in prison and upon release will
OL,16,Fbe subject to a Sexual Harm Prevention
OL,17,FOrder, and placed on the sex offenders
OL,18,Fregister for life.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1778234502
OL,3,CAppeal for victims of sex-offender
OL,4,Cformer Bishop after further reports
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FSince the sentencing, South Wales
OL,8,FPolice confirmed they received three
OL,9,Ffurther reports of offences dating
OL,10,Fback to the 1970s and 80s, which are
OL,11,Fcurrently under investigation.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Detective Inspector
OL,14,FTom Richardson of Swansea CID said:
OL,15,F"We know how difficult it must be for
OL,16,Fanyone to have suffered abuse in the
OL,17,Fpast to come forward now. It was the
OL,18,Fbravery of the victim who reported
OL,19,FPierce's actions which was
OL,20,Finstrumental in bringing him to
OL,21,Fjustice.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1778234502
OL,3,CAppeal for victims of sex-offender
OL,4,Cformer Bishop after further reports
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,F"Since the conviction and sentencing
OL,8,Fof Pierce we have received reports
OL,9,Ffrom three people who have taken that
OL,10,Ffirst step in coming forward.
OL,12,F"We believe that there may be others
OL,13,Fwho have been subject to Pierce's
OL,14,Fcrimes and we want to provide
OL,15,Freassurance that any reports will be
OL,16,Ffully investigated and dealt with
OL,17,Fsensitively and with compassion.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
