PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1778234502
OL,3,CAppeal for victims of sex-offender
OL,4,Cformer Bishop after further reports
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,F"We recognise that coming forward can
OL,8,Fbe daunting but would encourage victim-
OL,9,Fsurvivors to speak with us so they can
OL,10,Fget the support and help they deserve."
